  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `erigon version 2022.08.2-alpha-35c4faa1`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\nCommit hash : `git_commit=35c4faa1b41e8379a74d0385505add0dd450c2ed`\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nKeeping up to date with new blocks\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nAfter syncing blocks which are older then current time, erigon stops syncing newer ones\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n1. Run erigon with above mentioned version \r\n2. Wait for sync of older blockls\r\n3. Erigon will stop catching newer ones\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\nLogs are in attachment\r\n[bsc.log](https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/files/9476290/bsc.log)\r\n",
